<text><body>
<cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">頌古</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<milestone n="9" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0782a" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0782a"/>
<lb n="0782a01" ed="J"/><cb:mulu n="9" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:juan n="9" fun="open"><cb:jhead>入就瑞白禪師語錄卷之九</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0782a02" ed="J"/><byline cb:type="editor">明住天台護國寺嗣法門人寂蘊編</byline>
<lb n="0782a03" ed="J"/><p cb:type="head1" xml:id="pJ26p0782a0301">頌古</p>
<lb n="0782a04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a0401" style="margin-left:2em">正偏五位</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a0501">正中偏夜深，玉女不成眠，漁翁舉棹清波上，攪動澄
<lb n="0782a06" ed="J"/>潭月一團。</p>
<lb n="0782a07" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a0701">偏中正，萬象森羅圓古鏡，物物全彰炤不差，絲毫皆
<lb n="0782a08" ed="J"/>入那伽定。</p>
<lb n="0782a09" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a0901">正中來，有無，不涉絕塵埃。炎天大雪飄飄墜，火裏蓮
<lb n="0782a10" ed="J"/>花朵朵開。</p>
<lb n="0782a11" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1101">兼中至，賓主相逄天然義，全憑語脈露單傳一句當
<lb n="0782a12" ed="J"/>陽明的的。</p>
<lb n="0782a13" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1301">兼中到，打碎髑髏真個妙，劫外今時俱不拈，那有毘
<lb n="0782a14" ed="J"/>盧印可寶？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782a15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1501" style="margin-left:2em">功勳五位</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782a16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1601">本無位次絕參商，也須移履下村庄，六戶靈靈忘死
<lb n="0782a17" ed="J"/>捨，何勞守住在枯樁。　　向</p>
<lb n="0782a18" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1801">念念無私不敢迷，百花叢裏看為持，千紅萬紫芬芳
<lb n="0782a19" ed="J"/>好，總屬東君一道施。　　奉</p>
<lb n="0782a20" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2001">不居空有謾商量，縱使離婁眼似盲，無孔鐵簫雲外
<lb n="0782a21" ed="J"/>品，不干六律與宮商。　　功</p>
<lb n="0782a22" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2201">心色相交理事融，權施應物道人風。昨日家童頻報
<lb n="0782a23" ed="J"/>道，葵花傾向日明中。　　共功</p>
<lb n="0782a24" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2401">不向威音那畔行，豈從今世門頭立？渾然打破舊時
<lb n="0782a25" ed="J"/>窩，鐵鷂鑽天沒蹤跡。　　功功</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2601" style="margin-left:2em">奪人不奪境</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782a27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2701">一樹碧桃紅似錦，兩瓶金菊賽金蓮，個中非是陰陽
<lb n="0782a28" ed="J"/>地，不許<note n="0782a2801" resp="CBETA" type="add">佳【CB】，隹【嘉興】</note><app n="0782a2801"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">佳</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">隹</rdg></app>人著眼看。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782a29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2901" style="margin-left:2em">奪境不奪人</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782a30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a3001">春風疑不到天涯，二月山城未見花。公子王孫徒翫
<pb n="0782b" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0782b"/>
<lb n="0782b01" ed="J"/>賞，那有紅紫帶回家？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0201" style="margin-left:2em">人境兩俱奪</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0301">天崩地裂人民喪，那有君王正令行，神劍亡鋒歸寶
<lb n="0782b04" ed="J"/>匣，生佛而今徒有名。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0501" style="margin-left:2em">人境俱不奪</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0601">攜酒遊東郊，山花遍地紅，笑談歌舞去，意氣自匆匆。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0701" style="margin-left:2em">三玄三要</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0801">第一玄，動靜不干絕眾緣，更闌萬籟聲俱寂，禪者徒
<lb n="0782b09" ed="J"/>勞著眼看。</p>
<lb n="0782b10" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1001">第二玄，威風凜凜劍光寒，紅旗閃爍乾坤淨，電轉星
<lb n="0782b11" ed="J"/>飛過碧天。</p>
<lb n="0782b12" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1201">第三玄，越州城裏倒撐船。東雙橋下多裝載，西郭門
<lb n="0782b13" ed="J"/>頭去復還。</p>
<lb n="0782b14" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1401">朕兆未分作麼道？石女頭戴紫羅帽，深閨不出冷愀
<lb n="0782b15" ed="J"/>愀，宮漏沉沉天未曉。<note place="inline">一</note></p>
<lb n="0782b16" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1601">一法元無萬法周，喝下何曾有去留，轉側木人剛半
<lb n="0782b17" ed="J"/>夜，珍衣不掛柳稍頭。<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0782b18" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1801">日出峰頭本自孤，高低普炤有於無，百花競秀爭光
<lb n="0782b19" ed="J"/>彩。半點工夫用得麼？<note place="inline">三</note></p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2001" style="margin-left:2em">一喝如金剛王寶劍</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2101">神威凜凜倚天寒，阿個男兒敢近看，擬議欲將佛祖
<lb n="0782b22" ed="J"/>現，人亡馬喪滿長安。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2301" style="margin-left:2em">一喝如踞地獅子</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2401">全身獨露沖寰宇，那有妖狐現本形？一吼乾坤皆振
<lb n="0782b25" ed="J"/>裂，個中誰是對機人？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2601" style="margin-left:2em">一喝如探竿影艸</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2701">試將一語知端的，驗彼來人有與無，穿過髑髏行正
<lb n="0782b28" ed="J"/>令，神嚎鬼哭兩眉<g ref="#CB09432"/>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2901" style="margin-left:2em">一喝不作一喝用</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782b30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b3001">喝時秪麼忘消息，佛祖機緣收不得。野鴨湖中翻浪
<pb n="0782c" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0782c"/>
<lb n="0782c01" ed="J"/>飛，不知身上乾和濕。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0201" style="margin-left:2em">賓主歷然</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0301">月色穿雲透碧霄，波斯夜半舞風濤，山頭白浪連天
<lb n="0782c04" ed="J"/>地，石女經行俏步高。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0501" style="margin-left:2em">正法眼藏</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0601">掃除空有任繁興，大地山河一掌平，法法頭頭開正
<lb n="0782c07" ed="J"/>眼，寒崖花發不沾春。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0801" style="margin-left:2em">妙唱不干舌</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0901">青松翠竹解談禪，流水高山總亦然，二六時中無間
<lb n="0782c10" ed="J"/>斷，老僧何用口唇宣？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1101" style="margin-left:2em">死蛇驚出艸</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1201">骨爛皮穿氣息無，忽然撞著爪牙舒。神威一振清四
<lb n="0782c13" ed="J"/>海，狼煙滅盡豈躊躕？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1401" style="margin-left:2em">解針枯骨吟</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1501">鐵圍山下骨一堆，些兒觸著振全威，驚回石女雙流
<lb n="0782c16" ed="J"/>淚，至今猶自倚雲飛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1701" style="margin-left:2em">鐵牛舞三台</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1801">千載鐵牛忘水草，而今放出兩岸來，足伸踏破毘盧
<lb n="0782c19" ed="J"/>印，尾搖掃盡九垓灰。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c20" ed="J"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0782c2001">三墮頌<note place="inline">并問荅</note></p><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2007" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">僧問：如何是類墮？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2101">師荅云：觸處逍遙，絲毫無染。</p>
<lb n="0782c22" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2201">披毛戴角混塵埃，足舞西風類莫該，芳草垂楊俱踏
<lb n="0782c23" ed="J"/>遍，渾無些子帶回來。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2401" style="margin-left:1em">問：如何是隨墮？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2501">荅云：百花林裏過，一葉不沾身。</p>
<lb n="0782c26" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2601">聲色叢中任意遊，鬨然出沒豈能收？山花鳥語縱橫
<lb n="0782c27" ed="J"/>現，何有纖毫染污尤？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2801" style="margin-left:1em">問：如何是尊貴墮？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0782c29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2901">荅云：不住九五位，常與群臣遊。</p>
<lb n="0782c30" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c3001">虛寂靈源不自尊，常隨六國走煙塵，秦樓玩月燕邦
<pb n="0783a" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0783a"/>
<lb n="0783a01" ed="J"/>戲，到處逍遙到處人。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a02" ed="J"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0783a0201">涅槃經四生頌<note place="inline">并問荅</note></p><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0210" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">僧問：如何是不生生？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0301">師荅云：冬至纔逢九，春來百花開。</p>
<lb n="0783a04" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0401">明淨摩尼珠，本來無一物，當臺鑒炤時，隨處陳方色。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0501" style="margin-left:1em">問：如何是生生？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0601">荅云：青山點翠。</p>
<lb n="0783a07" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0701">忽然一陣雨，溪澗長洪波，枯稿悉滋潤，農人笑呵呵。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0801" style="margin-left:1em">問：如何是生不生？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0901">荅云：境像收歸古鑒中。</p>
<lb n="0783a10" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1001">桃李花無豔，遊人興自衰，水中無月影，免使費心裁。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1101" style="margin-left:1em">問：如何是不生不生？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1201">荅云：石女打破鏡。</p>
<lb n="0783a13" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1301">石女忘歸路，木人何處尋？杳然無影跡，佛祖莫能形。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1401" style="margin-left:2em">就路還家</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1501">觸目青黃露本真，縱橫到處是家珍，水底金烏天上
<lb n="0783a16" ed="J"/>口，眼中童子面前人。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1701" style="margin-left:2em">新<note n="0783a1701" resp="CBETA" type="add">豐【CB】，豊【嘉興】</note><app n="0783a1701"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">豐</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">豊</rdg></app>曲子</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1801">昔日新<note n="0783a1801" resp="CBETA" type="add">豐【CB】，豊【嘉興】</note><app n="0783a1801"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">豐</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">豊</rdg></app>曲，無人和得齊。今朝重舉似，音韻果然奇。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1901" style="margin-left:2em">明月印蘆花</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2001">蘆花開遍野，明月挂中天，不識其中意，都言一色然。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2101" style="margin-left:2em">鏡裏梅花清香墮</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2201">石光閃若電，渴鹿逐陽燄，木女害相思，泥人繡花絹。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2301" style="margin-left:2em">竭盡今時</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2401">真如心裏妄，涅槃性上塵，自<note n="0783a2401" resp="CBETA" type="add">己【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0783a2401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">己</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>非堪寶，佛祖是閒名。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2501" style="margin-left:2em">分明月在梅花上，看到梅花早<note n="0783a2501" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0783a2501"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>遲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2601">一段風光炤眼鮮，何須攜手入桃園？運足<note n="0783a2601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0783a2601"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>乖空劫
<lb n="0783a27" ed="J"/>旨，擬尋思去隔天淵。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2801" style="margin-left:2em">汾陽重陽九日菊花新</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783a29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2901">義公拈出膠盆，汾陽不覺粘手，賴因菊底翻身不然，
<lb n="0783a30" ed="J"/>甚麼開口不開口，木人捧起盤兒走。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0783b" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0783b"/>
<lb n="0783b01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0101" style="margin-left:2em">重陽日頌示禪人</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0201">重陽九日菊花新，特示三玄意旨深，報爾知音禪衲
<lb n="0783b03" ed="J"/>子，今朝籬菊又重芬。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0401" style="margin-left:2em">法身</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0501">雲起山頭暗，風生樹搖尾，桃開三月花，菊綻九日蕊。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0601" style="margin-left:2em">法身向上事</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0701">鐵樹花開正是時，忽被石女摘一枝，沙神怒發須彌
<lb n="0783b08" ed="J"/>倒，驚起泥龍上玉池。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0901" style="margin-left:2em">萬象之中獨露身</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1001">赫赫威音外，獨超萬象先，明明無隱匿，何處有三玄？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1101" style="margin-left:2em">法界緣起</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1201">一波纔動萬波隨，滴滴全彰造化機。落葉梧桐秋<note n="0783b1201" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0783b1201"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>
<lb n="0783b13" ed="J"/>蚤。百花開處鷓鴣啼。須領略，莫狐疑。翠竹搖聲兮風
<lb n="0783b14" ed="J"/>生大野，月映寒潭兮碧水畫眉。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1501" style="margin-left:1em">僧問百丈超云：某甲今日辭去，或有人問：和尚說
<lb n="0783b16" ed="J"/>甚麼法？向他道甚麼？超云：但道大雄山頂上，虎生
<lb n="0783b17" ed="J"/>獅子兒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1801">虎生獅子兒，木人唱巴歌，擬議停思者，卻被佛祖呵。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1901" style="margin-left:1em">僧問：明炤安一藏圓光。如何是體？安云：勞汝遠來。
<lb n="0783b20" ed="J"/>僧云：莫便是一藏圓光麼？安云：更喫一碗茶。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2101">問：處分明荅處彰，圓光之體露堂堂。春風布遍山花
<lb n="0783b22" ed="J"/>早，秋氣臨時樹葉黃。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2301" style="margin-left:1em">僧問：百丈惟政禪師云：牛頭未見四祖時，為甚麼
<lb n="0783b24" ed="J"/>百鳥啣花獻？師云：有錢千里通云：見後為甚麼不
<lb n="0783b25" ed="J"/>啣花？師云：無錢隔壁聾。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2601">一段春光炤眼鮮，攀花弄柳任溪邊，時人須識東君
<lb n="0783b27" ed="J"/>意，莫向枝頭覓翠妍。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2801" style="margin-left:2em">百丈普請鉏地次，僧聞鼓鳴歸院因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783b29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2901">鼓聲纔動競頭奔，卉木俱霑雨露。恩重勘過眼中釘，
<lb n="0783b30" ed="J"/>百花叢裏覓鮮新。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0783c" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0783c"/>
<lb n="0783c01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0101" style="margin-left:2em">百丈因一僧哭入法堂因緣</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0201">哭上法堂，草深一丈，一時埋卻野狐伎倆，匝匝清風
<lb n="0783c03" ed="J"/>撲面來，舒襟樂意頻收放。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0401" style="margin-left:2em">百丈惟政禪師問南泉：諸方善知識，還有不說
<lb n="0783c05" ed="J"/>似人底法也無？泉曰：有。政曰：作麼生？泉曰：不是
<lb n="0783c06" ed="J"/>心，不是佛，不是物<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0701">一問一荅，真機漏洩。更欲重徵，喬木生節。寒凝遍佈
<lb n="0783c08" ed="J"/>兮霜花朵朵，黃葉飄零兮朔風凜冽。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0901" style="margin-left:1em">僧問：百丈智映寶月禪師云：師唱誰家曲？宗風嗣
<lb n="0783c10" ed="J"/>阿誰？月云：窣堵那吒掌上擎<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1101">窣堵掌上擎，覿面<note n="0783c1101" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0783c1101"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>分付，更欲問如何，特地成露布。
<lb n="0783c12" ed="J"/>不露布初生，孩子元無褲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1301" style="margin-left:2em">百丈道恒禪師三訣因緣</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1401">喫茶，珍重歇時人眼中屑。若喚作三訣，重添第二月。
<lb n="0783c15" ed="J"/>穿衣褁腳下禪床，運水搬柴知時節。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1601" style="margin-left:2em">百丈惟古禪師上堂多虛不如少實</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1701">一卓一語，機用雙舉，更問如何，大虫捉鼠。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1801" style="margin-left:2em">百丈中靖元肅禪師塔</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1901">尖尖聳青虛，巍巍磨太古。欲識渠儂言，但看清風舞。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2001" style="margin-left:2em">漁家傲題船子夾山因緣</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2101">一語合頭猶未徹，禪師笑倒纔方革，劈面三橈君<note n="0783c2101" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0783c2101"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>
<lb n="0783c22" ed="J"/>瞥。眼中屑，回顧頻頻繫木橛。</p>
<lb n="0783c23" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2301">覆卻舟兒真剿絕，夾山從此偷心歇。兩岸蘆花飛白
<lb n="0783c24" ed="J"/>雪，向誰說幾度？秋光與明月。</p>
<lb n="0783c25" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2501" style="margin-left:2em">又頌</p>
<lb n="0783c26" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2601">金鱗<note n="0783c2601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0783c2601"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>遇意偏攸，誠老何曾覆卻舟？萬古清風波浪
<lb n="0783c27" ed="J"/>吼，依然蘭棹在中流。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2801" style="margin-left:1em">僧問夢筆禪師：如何是佛？師云：不誑汝。僧云：莫便
<lb n="0783c29" ed="J"/>是麼？師云：汝誑他。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0783c30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c3001">寂寂沉沉無所倚，全提覿面莫能擬，春風散盡桃花
<pb n="0784a" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0784a"/>
<lb n="0784a01" ed="J"/>飛，秋月影臨江水止。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a0201" style="margin-left:1em">閩王延夢筆禪師齋，王問曰：好將得筆來也無？師
<lb n="0784a03" ed="J"/>云：不是稽山繡管，慚非月裏兔毫。大王既垂顧問，
<lb n="0784a04" ed="J"/>山僧敢不通呈？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a0501">覿面通呈非兔毫，輕分閩主不辭勞。梅花吐處春香
<lb n="0784a06" ed="J"/>露，煦日纔臨冰質消。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a0701" style="margin-left:1em">王又曰：如何是法王？師曰：不是夢筆家風。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a0801">不是家風一句機，偷香暗裏有誰知？千峰布列須彌
<lb n="0784a09" ed="J"/>勢，萬派宗分大海歸。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a10" ed="J"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0784a1001">雲門三種獅子<note place="inline">師居雲門室中作</note></p>
<lb n="0784a11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1101" style="margin-left:1em">入窟獅子</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1201"><note n="0784a1201" resp="CBETA" type="add">斂【CB】，歛【嘉興】</note><app n="0784a1201"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">斂</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">歛</rdg></app>跡藏形古壑中，豈尋聲色受華榮？聖凡掃卻無依
<lb n="0784a13" ed="J"/>倚，斗柄星河霽碧空。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1401" style="margin-left:2em">出窟獅子</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1501">爪牙抖擻望天關，哮吼一聲碧嶂寒，魔外不知何處
<lb n="0784a16" ed="J"/>去，威靈耿耿落人間。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1701" style="margin-left:2em">不出不入獅子</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1801">窟內未曾留形跡，人間那得有聲名？石筍抽條千丈
<lb n="0784a19" ed="J"/>碧，泥花發豔四時春。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a20" ed="J"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0784a2001">圓覺經頌</p>
<lb n="0784a21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2101" style="margin-left:2em">文殊章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2201">本起如來清淨因，桃紅柳綠一般春，凡夫不了元無
<lb n="0784a23" ed="J"/>我，病眼空花認作真。圓炤婆伽親指示，依然幻翳眼
<lb n="0784a24" ed="J"/>中生。文殊當下知消息，石女峰頭喚故人。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2501" style="margin-left:2em">普賢章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2601">幻化元來生覺心，春風微動水生鱗。時人但見波濤
<lb n="0784a27" ed="J"/>滾，豈識波濤全體真？有覺還同如幻立，若緣無覺鏡
<lb n="0784a28" ed="J"/>中痕。兩重公案都除卻，天柱峰頭蓮萼新。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2901" style="margin-left:2em">普眼章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784a30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a3001">漸次修行滅幻門，火風地水究元辰，忽然突出孃生
<pb n="0784b" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0784b"/>
<lb n="0784b01" ed="J"/>面，剎剎塵塵總是春。擲柳黃鶯歌上苑，穿花杜宇遶
<lb n="0784b02" ed="J"/>南林。泥人翫月思情美，石女簪花巧樣新。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b0301" style="margin-left:2em">金剛藏章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b0401">金剛抉破三疑網，幻戲場中脫卻衣。若說本來成佛
<lb n="0784b05" ed="J"/>道，挖瘡好肉事非宜。只因蒙昧難開曉，金喻重重說
<lb n="0784b06" ed="J"/>是非。識得上林花滿地，風翻蝶舞過東籬。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b0701" style="margin-left:2em">彌勒章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b0801">起心若欲斷輪迴，荊棘叢生覺地迷夢去。雖然諸種
<lb n="0784b09" ed="J"/>事，醒來何有半毫微？若能寤寐都拈<note n="0784b0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">卻【CB】，郤【嘉興】</note><app n="0784b0901"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">卻</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">郤</rdg></app>，撒手懸崖好
<lb n="0784b10" ed="J"/>作為。銕犬山中呼萬歲，泥猿樹上唱囉哩。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1101" style="margin-left:2em">清淨慧章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1201">聲聞魔佛及菩薩，正眼觀來總是邪，朕兆未分難話
<lb n="0784b13" ed="J"/>會，鴻濛<note n="0784b1301" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0784b1301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>判念心差。千紅萬紫筵青嶂，總是陽春一
<lb n="0784b14" ed="J"/>氣嘉，踢破乾坤收腳轉，回頭別有好生涯。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1501" style="margin-left:2em">威德自在章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1601">突出乾城三觀門，止啼黃葉卻非真，新人乍出梳粧
<lb n="0784b17" ed="J"/>巧，莫認衣裳要認人。戲水遊魚知水意，穿花蝴蝶味
<lb n="0784b18" ed="J"/>花深，長安一曲有餘樂，野老君王共太平。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1901" style="margin-left:2em">辨音章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2001">二十五輪遍互修，一輪於內作根繇，列開寶網光相
<lb n="0784b21" ed="J"/>映，影現重重無盡頭。四塞八蠻朝帝主，兩京七地總
<lb n="0784b22" ed="J"/>皇猷，鄉村野老茶鹽足，一曲昇平樂事稠。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2301" style="margin-left:2em">淨諸業障章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2401">萬象收歸古鑑中，我人生命盡消融，空中飛鳥無形
<lb n="0784b25" ed="J"/>跡，水底遊魚有甚蹤？出岫浮雲何處往？乘風花瓣任
<lb n="0784b26" ed="J"/>西東。回頭忽聽木人鼓，魄散魂飛沒影蹤。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2701" style="margin-left:2em">普覺章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784b28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2801">作止任滅聽從為，休將四法取圓基，平懷一種隨高
<lb n="0784b29" ed="J"/>下，大道從來沒是非。碧嶂野花開似錦，石人觀去絕
<lb n="0784b30" ed="J"/>惺迷。妙開寶印空中起，印印何曾半點非？</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0784c" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0784c"/>
<lb n="0784c01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0101" style="margin-left:2em">圓覺章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0201">上下中期結制修，鈍根須假煆塵浮。大鵬翼展沖霄
<lb n="0784c03" ed="J"/>漢，豈類鴳鶉落草坵？十世古今頃一念，誰能百日定
<lb n="0784c04" ed="J"/>程途？狸奴白牯咸知有，飢則餐兮渴飲流。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0501" style="margin-left:2em">賢善首章</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0601">三世如來一口宣，流傳須要善賢兼，能聞一句勝多
<lb n="0784c07" ed="J"/>寶，羅漢難同半偈肩。不是天然生就覺，又非觀行始
<lb n="0784c08" ed="J"/>成圓。鷺鷥昨夜沙汀宿，分付漁翁仔細看。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0901" style="margin-left:2em">總</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1001">一道靈光貫古今，剎塵俱是一毛吞，獨超物表離名
<lb n="0784c11" ed="J"/>相，阿個能言圓覺心。一自伽婆分旨後，千燈千炤續
<lb n="0784c12" ed="J"/>燈新。孑蘆隨海飄波去，熊耳峰頭花滿岑。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c13" ed="J"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0784c1301">首楞嚴經要頌</p>
<lb n="0784c14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1401" style="margin-left:2em">大佛頂</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1501">三德圓明非形相，直教佛祖也難觀。一聲胡笛邊營
<lb n="0784c16" ed="J"/>外，幾處凄涼幾處歡？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1701" style="margin-left:2em">首楞嚴王</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1801">一相該通空劫前，河沙功德孰能宣？超然不屬青黃
<lb n="0784c19" ed="J"/>色，了了無依當處玄。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2001" style="margin-left:2em">七處徵心</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2101">七處徵來七處真，鷓鴣啼在百花林，遊人沉醉桃園
<lb n="0784c22" ed="J"/>裡，昧卻枝頭好鳥音。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2301" style="margin-left:2em">五陰</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2401">真如迷卻翻成妄，相妄空時當處真，收拾伽缶歸去
<lb n="0784c25" ed="J"/>後，白牛耕破劫前春。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2601" style="margin-left:2em">六入</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2701">一團空聚無彼此，痴兒妄自別疏親。堂堂天子登朝
<lb n="0784c28" ed="J"/>日，六國文明賀太平。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2901" style="margin-left:2em">十二處</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0784c30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c3001">塵塵三昧首楞嚴，擬心取著早乖遷。月穿潭底非形
<pb n="0785a" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0785a"/>
<lb n="0785a01" ed="J"/>相，痴子徒勞摸碧川。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0201" style="margin-left:2em">十八界</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0301">本來一相無疆界，那許其間物我分。十八疑關齊擊
<lb n="0785a04" ed="J"/>碎，滔滔流水下滄溟。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0501" style="margin-left:2em">七大</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0601">事理交參周法界，將心擬處涉流沙，情塵識破元無
<lb n="0785a07" ed="J"/>事，木馬遊春意自賒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0801" style="margin-left:2em">聲塵圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0901">妙音本自無來去，聞聲悟入<note n="0785a0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0785a0901"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>成虛，直須透徹聲前
<lb n="0785a10" ed="J"/>韻，浩浩紅塵任卷舒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1101" style="margin-left:2em">色塵圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1201">色色塵塵淨法身，秪因憎愛昧天真，苟能觸處通消
<lb n="0785a13" ed="J"/>息，堪笑沙陀入聖倫。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1401" style="margin-left:2em">香塵圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1501">妙香元不從天降，爇向爐中塞碧虛，觸著些兒頭腦
<lb n="0785a16" ed="J"/>裂，衲僧巴鼻盡蠲除。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1701" style="margin-left:2em">味塵圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1801">古今一味平胃散，點著通身冷汗流，慶快怡然拋藥
<lb n="0785a19" ed="J"/>病，那容更犯死貓頭？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2001" style="margin-left:2em">觸塵圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2101">能洗所洗性本然，驀頭一潑觸光圓，器界根身渾一
<lb n="0785a22" ed="J"/>色，輝輝秋月炤中天。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2301" style="margin-left:2em">法塵圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2401">心緣既寂法塵空，事事全彰振古風。東嶺桃花紅爍
<lb n="0785a25" ed="J"/>爍，西溪流水響鼕鼕。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2601" style="margin-left:2em">眼根圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2701">見色非關眼上能，時人休向眼中親。應知那律非循
<lb n="0785a28" ed="J"/>目，智鑑圓明耀古今。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2901" style="margin-left:2em">耳根圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785a30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a3001">反觀聞性性俱空，頓入圓明顯妙功，歷歷松聲連夜
<pb n="0785b" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0785b"/>
<lb n="0785b01" ed="J"/>吼，呱呱鳥語亂山中。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0201" style="margin-left:2em">鼻根圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0301">循空返息本非真，翻身踏倒涅槃城。紅日舒光來嶺
<lb n="0785b04" ed="J"/>畔，清風明月過溪濱。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0501" style="margin-left:2em">舌根圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0601">身心世界兩相遺，覿體全超知不知，處處總成真法
<lb n="0785b07" ed="J"/>界，禪兒何事苦尋追？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0801" style="margin-left:2em">身根圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0901">無痛痛覺覺亦空，根身從此影無蹤，出門不踏來時
<lb n="0785b10" ed="J"/>路，方顯男兒志氣沖。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1101" style="margin-left:2em">意根圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1201">物物頭頭本自真，何須旋法美空生？寶明空海人元
<lb n="0785b13" ed="J"/>具，桃李爭妍處處春。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1401" style="margin-left:2em">眼識圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1501">心見圓明處處彰，白雲閒矣水偏忙，為憐頞下生盲
<lb n="0785b16" ed="J"/>者，權示漚和演妙常。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1701" style="margin-left:2em">耳識圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1801">無心聞處是心聞，塵剎全彰這個人，百億分身無去
<lb n="0785b19" ed="J"/>相，六牙常在寶王城。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2001" style="margin-left:2em">鼻識圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2101">鼻端白相示修行，暫爾權為縳犢繩，忽然摸著娘生
<lb n="0785b22" ed="J"/>鼻，林泉巖谷悉光明。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2301" style="margin-left:2em">舌識圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2401">奇哉妙舌自天然，不假喉唇齒吻宣。無孔笛吹清韻
<lb n="0785b25" ed="J"/>徹，滿慈謾謂得親傳。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2601" style="margin-left:2em">身識圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2701">身本無根何用執？心本無生何用息？身心寂滅兩俱
<lb n="0785b28" ed="J"/>空，透此方名真法質。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2901" style="margin-left:2em">意識圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b3001">一段情城當下除，神通遊戲總無拘，塢中昨日濛濛
<pb n="0785c" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0785c"/>
<lb n="0785c01" ed="J"/>雨，嶺上今朝日色舒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0201" style="margin-left:2em">地大圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0301">根身器界若微塵，微塵空處即天真，堪<note n="0785c0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">羨【CB】，羡【嘉興】</note><app n="0785c0301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">羨</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">羡</rdg></app>頂門開正
<lb n="0785c04" ed="J"/>眼，大千沙界一齊平。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0501" style="margin-left:2em">水大圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0601">滔滔流水性真常，若個於斯返故鄉，直於山海忘能
<lb n="0785c07" ed="J"/>所，蝴蝶穿花過粉墻。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0801" style="margin-left:2em">火大圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0901">凡火慾火智慧火，清淨寶焰光裸裸，大千閃爍熾穹
<lb n="0785c10" ed="J"/>窿，燃卻佛魔與物我。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1101" style="margin-left:2em">風大圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1201">群動悉憑風力持，反觀風力亦無依，忽然踏著風中
<lb n="0785c13" ed="J"/>主，飄飄一葉過南池。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1401" style="margin-left:2em">空大圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1501">色空本自一真空，逐境迷心有異同，異同炤破真空
<lb n="0785c16" ed="J"/>現，翻轉真空跨鐵龍。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1701" style="margin-left:2em">見大圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1801">六根清淨生元佛，六根妄染佛為生，見覺圓明生佛
<lb n="0785c19" ed="J"/>淨，個中那有樂邦名？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2001" style="margin-left:2em">識大圓通</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2101">十方唯識鏡中痕，但離取捨妙圓成，頭頭盡是天真
<lb n="0785c22" ed="J"/>佛，念念全彰阿逸身。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2301" style="margin-left:2em">圓滿菩提，歸無所得。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2401">元宵通夜家家火，水月交光處處圓，五十七番虛涉
<lb n="0785c25" ed="J"/>後，始知空費草鞋錢。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2601" style="margin-left:2em">總</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2701">二十五個鐵蒺藜，頭阤拶作雪花飛，綠水溶溶歸巨
<lb n="0785c28" ed="J"/>壑，白雲片片遶須彌。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785c29" ed="J"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0785c2901">金剛經要頌</p>
<lb n="0785c30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c3001" style="margin-left:2em">世尊著衣持缽</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0786a" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0786a"/>
<lb n="0786a01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0101">一段風光秪在斯，著他依舊不為奇。清風陣陣飄香
<lb n="0786a02" ed="J"/>至，碧水滔滔畫翠眉。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0301" style="margin-left:2em">應如是住</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0401">搬柴運水尋常事，覿面無非是道場，觸處盡成安樂
<lb n="0786a05" ed="J"/>地，何須此外更<note n="0786a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">商【CB】，啇【嘉興】</note><app n="0786a0501"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">商</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">啇</rdg></app>量？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0601" style="margin-left:2em">如是降伏其心</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0701">著衣喫飯，任從為映。色摩尼眾像，隨但得有無，諸念
<lb n="0786a08" ed="J"/>淨金烏，依舊落城西。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0901" style="margin-left:2em">實無眾生得滅度者</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1001">空花鏡像了無關，擬欲援生墮鐵山。踏破瞿曇關捩
<lb n="0786a11" ed="J"/>子，風自清兮雲自閒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1201" style="margin-left:2em">不住於相</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1301">祖印高提不住中，巍然大用有無空。騰騰任運靡存
<lb n="0786a14" ed="J"/>跡，霧鎖秦宮絕雁鴻。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1501" style="margin-left:2em">應無所住而生其心</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1601">坐斷兩頭中莫立，逢緣擊節任縱橫，摩尼現色原非
<lb n="0786a17" ed="J"/>有，石筍開花映水紅。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1801" style="margin-left:2em">無我、人、眾生、壽者</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1901">木子山中敲鼓鑼，泥人拍手助高歌，忽逢瞽叟來瞧
<lb n="0786a20" ed="J"/>見，滿面慚惶沒柰何。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2101" style="margin-left:2em">四果不作是念</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2201">設分位次隔參商，息卻名心絕短長。若是威音親嫡
<lb n="0786a23" ed="J"/>子，不從這裡費<note n="0786a2301" resp="CBETA" type="add">商【CB】，啇【嘉興】</note><app n="0786a2301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">商</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">啇</rdg></app>量。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2401" style="margin-left:2em">燃燈佛所於法實無所得</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2501">倚門傍戶走他鄉，雲水將來作道場，倏爾踏翻潭底
<lb n="0786a26" ed="J"/>月，了無一法贈劉郎。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2701" style="margin-left:2em">持四句偈，得福甚多。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2801">家藏白澤勝神符，百怪安能敢穢污，若得空王真號
<lb n="0786a29" ed="J"/>令，三千諸佛作驅奴。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786a30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a3001" style="margin-left:2em">歌利王割截身體</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0786b" ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0786b"/>
<lb n="0786b01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0101">忍辱功能作聖人，幻成四大卻非真，任他節節支離
<lb n="0786b02" ed="J"/>去，一段風流獨露身。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0301" style="margin-left:2em">一念信心，即得菩提。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0401">棄家浪走不如屠，自昧千金七寶軀，偶爾忽逢長者
<lb n="0786b05" ed="J"/>示，凡心即與聖心符。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0601" style="margin-left:2em">「受持讀誦此經，若為人輕賤。」一節</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0701">念念輸忠不敢違，色聲叢裡了無羈，苔封古殿忘臣
<lb n="0786b08" ed="J"/>主，阿個能言佛祖機。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0901" style="margin-left:2em">三心不可得</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1001">兔角為刀出遠征，烏龜跨下羽毛生，木童拔去搓繩
<lb n="0786b11" ed="J"/>索，縛住虛空架火烹。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1201" style="margin-left:2em">無法可得</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1301">三藏靈文不較多，權將音語示娑婆，忽地雙林開正
<lb n="0786b14" ed="J"/>眼。試問還曾有也麼？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1501" style="margin-left:2em">如來說非眾生，是名眾生。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1601">生佛從來共一程，凡民何必<note n="0786b1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">羨【CB】，羡【嘉興】</note><app n="0786b1601"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">羨</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">羡</rdg></app>公卿，如能當下歸家
<lb n="0786b17" ed="J"/>也，凡聖原來是假名。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1801" style="margin-left:2em">如來者，無所從來，亦無所去。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1901">一念緣生即是遊，靡分紅紫有何愁？威音那畔元無
<lb n="0786b20" ed="J"/>動，今世門頭示兩眸。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2101" style="margin-left:2em">總</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2201">忉忉怛怛老婆禪，失卻瞿曇臉半邊，四相掃除無一
<lb n="0786b23" ed="J"/>物，呼名般若亦縺涎。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2401" style="margin-left:2em">法華經頌<note place="inline">二</note></p></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2501">三乘不立一也無，三一元來醒夢夫，若是空王殿上
<lb n="0786b26" ed="J"/>客，撒手歸來月滿湖。</p>
<lb n="0786b27" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2701">妙法不在聲名上，尊者徒勞授記功，欲識個中端的
<lb n="0786b28" ed="J"/>意，桃花卻白李花紅。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb n="0786b29" ed="J"/>
<lb n="0786b30" ed="J"/><cb:juan n="9" fun="close"><cb:jhead>入就瑞白禪師語錄卷之九終</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>